namespace Pizza

features
	Pizza {abstract}	
		mandatory
			Topping	
				or
					Salami
					Ham
					Mozzarella
			Size	
				alternative
					Normal
					Big
			Dough	
				alternative
					Neapolitan
					Sicilian

		optional
			CheesyCrust

constraints
	Big => Ham
	Neapolitan | Normal & Sicilian => !Size | Ham & CheesyCrust